    "After the catalog <em>Il Seicento Europeo</em>, 1956, written with Marabottini, he was promoted in 1958 to monuments director for Lazio (Soprintendenza ai monumenti del Lazio).": [],
    "There he researched and wrote on the urban history of Rome beginning with, <em>Altari barocchi</em> in 1959.": [],
