    "Together with <a href=\"/spezzaferrol\">Luigi Spezzaferro</a> and the architectural historian <a href=\"/tafurim\">Manfredo Tafuri</a>, the trio published <em>Via Giulia: una utopia urbanistica del 500</em> in 1973.": [],
